Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.07,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.15,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Time for your stamps!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, who's first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.82,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,The kitty's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.06,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,The kitty's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.38,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,The kitty's so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:38.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers seem to be full of life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:39.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:45.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did put my life\Non the line to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I went into the forest and\Ngot bitten by dogs to save the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,got bitten by dogs when I tried to save\NRem after she turned into a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:56.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,then had to be saved by Roswaal when I was about to be bitten by a giant dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:57.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:00.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did I even do anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:04.11,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Don't fuss\Nover the small details!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:06.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:09.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That includes Roswaal and Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.29,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And especially Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:12.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon-drawn carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:20.30,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:24.31,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me for parking \Nin front of your mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.99,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,An emissary is visiting from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:38.17,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal-sama is attending to them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.29,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama, please join him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:41.49,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,An emissary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.74,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it concerns the royal selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:51.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Given the circumstances, \NI'll try not to do anything dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.96,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm really sorry, Subaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:57.68,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but this will be a very important discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:13.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you bored waiting out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.20,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.66,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though I'm\Nindulging in a great luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually the most expensive \Ntea in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:29.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If the pink-haired maid learns we drank \Nit without permission, she'll flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:33.43,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,And what is it you hope to gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from this old man, using such precious bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I only want to know\Nthe reason for this visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you could just give me a vague idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.90,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,As I have no idea what your \Nstanding is in this mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.24,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot say anything careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:55.69,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,However, I did see that you are \Nquite close to Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did it look like things were serious \Nbetween Emilia-tan and me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:00.96,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,"Tan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.13,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,It is a steep path you climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:08.95,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You are dealing with one who may \Nbe Lugunica's future queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:14.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're just a super cute \Ngirl and a useless servant boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think your wife is \Nthe prettiest girl in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you thought \Nwhen you proposed to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.28,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.02,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. You are correct indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.85,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I believed my wife the most \Nbeautiful lady in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.81,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Old Man Wil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.26,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you were bored, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.31,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:43.32,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,This young man has been speaking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.77,Default,Feilx,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, {\i1}nyow{\i0} I see... Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.80,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the boy Emilia-sama mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.88,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you know {\i1}nyothing{\i0} at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.46,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Old Man Wil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.59,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,See you in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.82,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see, we aren't going for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:08.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I received an important summons—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it's important, all the more reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:15.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you in a battle for the \Nthrone? I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:15.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:22.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are people in the \Ncapital who helped Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.45,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a good opportunity \Nfor him to thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice assist, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Some people in the capital helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to let them know I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.80,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can be kept separate from \Nour royal selection business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:44.41,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun should go to the \Ncapital to thank everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.83,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,as well as to receive treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.41,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,You overused your already-exhausted \Ngate in the mabeast battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.29,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Treatment would tend that wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.41,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,You met the emissary earlier, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The cutesy-face with the cat ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:04.28,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,That was one of the capital's most \Nbrilliant users of water magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.05,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,as well as healing magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.40,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Felix is a peculiar character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:13.10,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Even Emilia-sama had difficulty \Nenlisting Felix's cooperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.80,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Emilia-tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You did that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:20.59,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's partly my fault that \Nyou haven't healed yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.06,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So you could say I'm repaying a debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's compensation equal to what you gave up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:32.39,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to see you\Ntalk with that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.76,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you preferred chopping people \Nin half than talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.04,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,That is a grave misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:41.11,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I merely took a bit of a liking \Nto that young man's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:48.00,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the eyes of one who has \Nexperienced death several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.77,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, you've lost me {\i1}nyow{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:56.60,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,But if Wilhelm van Astrea, \Nthe sword demon, says it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:00.37,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the boy faces quite a bumpy road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Emilia-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.61,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I look away, you'll be \Ndoing something crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.98,Default - flashback,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! I'm seriously moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.86,Default - flashback,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fantasying right now, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.73,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.19,Default - flashback,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Parallel worlds rul—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.11,Default - flashback,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But this is treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:38.29,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you wanted to hold \Nhands on our date in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was physically and\Nmentally prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand's sweating like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:47.01,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two quit\Nit with the flirting already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.05,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna drive away my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,After I came to make good on my promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.55,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I appreciate that\Nyou felt obliged to shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.06,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,now that you're not broke anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.06,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the appas I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Next, it's Felt and Old Man Rom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:10.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd wrapped things up \Nwithout blame the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But then Reinhard's expression went dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and he took the girl away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:19.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sound like kidnapping, \Nor an abduction and confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hot guys really have it good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to contact Reinhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:28.19,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,we should probably go to the guard station \Nin front of the district for the nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-tan, about the royal selection \Nthat begins tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:40.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you here to fulfill your \Npromises and to get you healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.61,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well since we last met?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.10,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everything is basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You also seem well, Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.76,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The mere fact that you\Nremember me is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:09.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You have only grown more\Nbeautiful, Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Forgive me for asking so abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:20.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But I have business here, and I'd like you \Nto act as my agent in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.88,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Does your business involve this young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:28.78,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,His character and attitude\Npoorly suit his attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.74,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to act before\None you've just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a warning for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't eat curry udon in that suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If the soup splatters, the stains \Nwill really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.40,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what "curry udon" is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I shall keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.50,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, allow me to show you \Nto the conference mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Conference mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:58.75,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A metia that facilitates talking with someone, \Nusing two mirrors facing one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, mirrors... How very magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.71,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it would be a pleasant \Nexperience for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've already had an experience \Nthat wasn't pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:16.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, licking all over your cute, \Nlittle hand, as if he owned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to come back before things run too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Be good and wait, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.43,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I look so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Doing that in front of the\Nguard station is bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"It's darkest at the\Nlighthouse's foot," I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:37.88,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.75,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.11,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Want us to mess up that pretty face of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.88,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such a racket, commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.52,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Fools with no character pick fights \Nfor the most foolish of reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It appears there's been a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But remember who I am,\Nand cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.09,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Do not touch me as if you know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Cliffhanger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:07.96,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want drooling commoners \Nto follow me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Recognize what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:14.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be a classic scenario \Nwhere I save a girl from hoodlums!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you three the capital's only hoodlums?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.54,Default,Ton,0000,0000,0000,,We met this guy in the alley \Nbehind the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.17,Default,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the brat from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, for my sake, could you just let us—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.10,Default,Kan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just makes it three on two, \Ninstead of three on one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.98,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,You should correct that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't three on two,\Nbut three on one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be quiet for a second?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.39,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.45,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last trick\NI wanted to use, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:47.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you, I know Reinhard-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I call for him, he'll come running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.22,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique: Fox in Tiger's Clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.03,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while since I've seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.50,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.17,Default,Three,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.77,Default,Three,0000,0000,0000,,We won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, Old Man Rom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt this girl and I\Ncould've handled that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.63,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:25.72,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Even without you two, I was in no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:32.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"I didn't need your help. I'm super \Nstrong! I was doing just fine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:33.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.74,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:38.03,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,This world is designed to operate in \Nthe way that works best for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.97,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,so I am never at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I shouldn't have butted in, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.32,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you know where Felt went off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Reinhard took her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.69,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:01.65,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be an Astrea, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.01,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, just talkin' to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.49,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,You try not to cause\Nany more trouble, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Emili—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:19.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just pick up Emilia-tan \Nwhile I'm away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Seems your buddy's got a \Nscrew loose, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,More worried about losing you to \Nanother man than happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,A man's heart is so complex,\Nit's a thrill to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a pretty messed-up \Nfashion sense of your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's no way to talk to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:41.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm a cool,\Ngood-natured man, I'll overlook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But some might lop off your head for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Subaru. His outfit surprised me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:55.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when she asked for my help\Nwhile I was looking for a lost child, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-tan, you're too soft-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Most would think a guy dressed like this \Nwas looking for a lost child to kidnap them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:06.86,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,My, how attentive you are to wait \Nwhere you knew I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.29,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,I commend your dedication, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You were the lost child?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like we both found the \Nones we were looking for. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.02,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.24,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,What is in that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They're appas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.45,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appas have white flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, the insides are white...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, s-so you've never\Nseen an unpeeled appa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't skip off after\Nany bad guys again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:48.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That girl from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you meet that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Emilia-tan? Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually getting jealous over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.32,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:10.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Emilia-tan, why the serious face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing... If you don't know, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.30,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It really is an appa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I have to stay here tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.10,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was our agreement all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we never reached Reinhard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So if we go to the castle tomorrow, \Nwe might see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to ask about Felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I should go in person to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.24,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why I can't take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.33,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, you'll push yourself too hard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to let you do that. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to push myself to help you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to push myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Until your body fully heals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no using magic or pushing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.22,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So let me go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring an outsider into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:28.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So please wait here with Rem, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me reason to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.76,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are those in the capital \Nwho consider Emilia an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.72,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to stay close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.81,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When you stare with such dramatic \Neyes, it makes me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.65,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.97,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.25,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,There will likely be heavy security, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Security isn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand not being involved \Nin Emilia's important affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only of any use when something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:36.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to be with her when \Nimportant things are going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:44.64,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I shall set about preparing a new \Nappa recipe I just thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.69,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It will require intense concentration,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.10,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,so if one were to leave his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I likely would not notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.80,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a scumbag for relying \Non Rem all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:05.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem is how I'm \Ngonna get into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess times like this call for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hitchhiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are lucky... Be grateful \Nfor this coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to be on our \Nway to the castle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The castle? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:27.19,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one reason to \Nhead to the castle today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This young lady here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:36.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,is one of the candidates to succeed \Nto the throne of Lugunica,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla Barielle-sama herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For real? Then why did you pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.25,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,For no other reason than it seemed amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.88,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,A mere lark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:50.96,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Taking you to the castle will \Nmake things interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.92,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,This world is designed to operate in \Nthe way that works best for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:01.93,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,so it's a given that all\Nthings work in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:06.89,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,It is only a matter of choosing whether \Nsomething amuses me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.73,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,However, if I had to name a reason \Nother than amusement...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.90,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Your appa handler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:22.60,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. He is something of a wretched clown,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:26.33,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,whose sole priority is to bring \Nme bittersweet red appas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.76,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is waiting inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:33.71,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Make haste, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:37.42,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,As their superior, it is my privilege \Nto keep the masses waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Emilia, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:05.49,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason you stare at \Nmy manservant, half-wit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Get off! You'll give\NEmilia-tan the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:11.36,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,My, how nice to see you, Priscilla-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:14.53,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Do forgive my servant for troubling you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to be good and wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.81,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,The council of wise men will now enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The wise men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:45.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They're the people managing the country \Nin the king's absence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. That's where we're supposed to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can stand there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.66,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.51,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds entertaining, so you \Nmay accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.06,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Roswaal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Subaru is allowed to stay, he'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.26,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama, the conference is beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You'll explain this to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those are the participants \Nin the royal selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The candidates for the future ruler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.40,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,You came, after all, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.10,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard Emilia-sama would be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.16,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected you'd be here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard, I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.04,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya, Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.27,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Subaru, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.89,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He is a knight, Felix Argyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:43.76,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Despite appearances, he is male.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:48.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a guy, what's the point in having \Nthose looks and even cat ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.44,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.86,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who made the wrong \Nassumption, Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.78,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'm from, this is the expression you \Nmake when seeing a romantic rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.12,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if I may be so forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.00,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,I, Marcos, leader of the Imperial Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will direct today's proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.96,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened about half a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.94,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,when members of the royal family, \Nstarting with the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.87,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,went into hiding, one by one, causing—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.68,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:30.26,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,I get that you wanna talk up a good \Nshow here, but I'm busy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.39,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,As we say in Kararagi, "Time is money."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the Kansai dialect? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.34,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you're just repeating\Nwhat we already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:41.11,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}then why did y'all even gather us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:41.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Evidently, everyone in western \NKararagi speaks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.66,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.08,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama, should the Karsten family \Nhead say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:49.18,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Observing formality is important, \Nbut it is also a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.33,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,that our time is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:55.96,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wise to inform us \Nwhy we are here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.00,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I do have a general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:02.25,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,You already know the purpose of this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.98,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Miklotov.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a drinking party, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.88,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,One day, we will face each other as rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:11.83,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But by sharing the same table and drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.97,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,we will learn about one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.85,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, this isn't what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:23.45,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I said was, \N"Maybe it'll be a drinking party."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.45,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.14,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. Allow me to \Nretract what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.53,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she backs down, \Nmy opinion isn't gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:41.55,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,No need to explain the royal selection now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:43.71,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:46.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should hear the—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:49.84,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I wasn't askin' your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:51.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:53.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's up with the selection, \Nso I'd kinda like to hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:01.81,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla-sama, I'm told\Nthis man is your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:04.35,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Have you explained the selection to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:09.07,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you men will\Nramble on about it, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.15,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Continue, Marcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.53,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:16.99,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,We've gathered you, who are qualified \Nto be the dragon's priestess,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:21.17,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,because a new prophecy has been \Nengraved in the Dragon Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.74,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "From the five capable of \Nbecoming the nation's new leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:29.97,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,choose one priestess to enter into \Na covenant with the dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:31.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.93,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:36.45,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, there are only four candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.78,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The royal selection hadn't even begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:42.10,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:44.61,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,history is set in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:48.57,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Knight Reinhard van Astrea, come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:49.33,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.95,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Honored members of the council of wise men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:24:00.68,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I, Reinhard van Astrea,\N of the Imperial Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:03.37,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,would like to announce\Nmy mission's completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.01,0:24:08.56,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon's priestess, the fifth and \Nfinal candidate for the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:11.59,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,has been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:25.06,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The one I, myself, revere as queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:27.77,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.18,0:24:31.15,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,is Felt-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:36.15,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8AD2FB&}Re{\c&HFFFFFF&}turn to the Capital
